  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 75–Uncomfortable Shoes.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第75课——不舒适的鞋子。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "What's wrong with the fashionable shoes?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "那些时髦的鞋有什么问题？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Do you have any shoes like these?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "你们有像这样的鞋吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "What size?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "几号的？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "Size five.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "5号。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "What color?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "什么颜色？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "Black.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "黑色。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "对不起。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "We don't have any.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我们没有。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "But my sister bought this pair last month.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "可我姐姐上个月买了这样一双。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "Did she buy them here?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她是在这里买的吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "No.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "不是。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "She bought them in the U.S.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她是在美国买的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "We had some shoes like those a month ago, but we don't have any now.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "一个月前我们有一些那样的鞋，但现在没有了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "Can you get a pair for me, please?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "能请您给我找一双吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "I'm afraid that I can't.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "恐怕不行。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "text": "They were in fashion last year, and the year before last, but they're not in fashion this year.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这种鞋去年和前年很流行，但今年不流行了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "text": "These shoes are in fashion now.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "现在流行的是这种鞋。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "text": "They look very uncomfortable.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "它们看起来很不舒服。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "text": "They are very uncomfortable, but women always wear uncomfortable shoes.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "的确很不舒服，但女人们总是穿不舒服的鞋。"
      }
    }
  ],
